description.en:
Zhu Xiao Ou originally wanted to live a life of suffering, waiting for the day that he would die, but he was suddenly asked to be the leader of a sect! A max level celestial master ancestor came down from the sky, and his handsomeness is off the charts! Relying on this master ancestor to support his back, Zhu Xiao Ou started to open the way to heaven, to earth and to the exotic flowers! Oh, Master ancestor even obtained the ability to reproduce, no matter if the other person is a female or male.

“Hey wait! Master ancestor, what are you doing to me!”
